{"tid":179322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲被控尋釁滋事明天再上庭受審","createTime":"2017-03-30T07:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T07:57:38.000Z","uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d63f87ed7e51d41a59877f456b66c0b8e1b5bb6","tid":179322,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:19:35.000Z","msg":"陳雲飛被控尋釁滋事明天再上庭受審<br />\n30.03.2017 14:36<br />\n四川維權人士陳雲飛，被控尋釁滋事罪，明日再在成都市武候區法院受審。他的代表律師郭海波說，今日會到看守所，與陳雲飛會面，為出庭做準備。<br />\n<br />\n曾經參與八九學運的陳雲飛，前年三月與二十多名成都公民，到成都市新津縣拜祭六四死難學生後，陳雲飛被公安帶走，之後被當局以尋釁滋事罪及煽動顛覆國家政權罪拘捕，檢察院其後撤銷了顛覆罪。"},{"pid":"fe0ef8a9431126e2014f385f0833fe79d71184fc","tid":179322,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29633bd65f9fdf035510660d85a70e22dc4503a","tid":179322,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/30/152743_52a37e718ebd5da0b7bdd378b00f1ded.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F30%2F152743_52a37e718ebd5da0b7bdd378b00f1ded.jpg&h=4dbc291d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a98d030c26803cf5179687c33f6211c26ef385cd","tid":179322,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"報得驚"},{"pid":"10eb02912e74f0196aadbfb58cff3ed420cc6c2b","tid":179322,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89694e1b29f287f4e65f73148a0e0bfd4fd74c3d","tid":179322,"uid":19552,"like":0,"disli